{"TopicId":184477,"ForumId":18,"TopicTitle":"Chernobyl (HBO)","CreatedByName":"tater","CreatedById":119411,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-14T04:58:57Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"tater","CreatedById":119411,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-14T04:58:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs simply awesome.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen this series is over, I certainly buy it, it\u0027s just fantastic.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-05-14T05:14:40Z\u0022 title=\u002205/14/2019 05:14  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EMay 14, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by tater\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Cydonian Monk","CreatedById":69224,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-14T17:08:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo far I\u0027m very impressed. Some creative liberties taken (such as consolidating thousands of scientists into one Belorussian character), but the first 2/5ths of it has been very very good.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Shpaget","CreatedById":45577,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-14T20:42:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHoley bubbling sluice water\u00A0cliffhanger in the second episode!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/119411-tater/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022119411\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/119411-tater/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@tater\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0for the recommendation.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Just Jim","CreatedById":148725,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-14T20:51:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI did not know about this... but if y\u0027all say it\u0027s good...\u003Cbr\u003E\nI just set it to record...\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tater","CreatedById":119411,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-14T20:52:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, I\u0027ve been really impressed. They take some artistic liberties as \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/69224-cydonian-monk/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002269224\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/69224-cydonian-monk/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Cydonian Monk\u003C/a\u003E mentions, but in the after show (they have a podcast as well), they explain them.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223598919\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184477\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557866534\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002245577\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Shpaget\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 minutes ago, Shpaget said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHoley bubbling sluice water\u00A0cliffhanger in the second episode!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2 of the divers were in fact in the military, but still cool. It\u0027s just so very well done.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://leatherbarrowa.exposure.co/chernobyl\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://leatherbarrowa.exposure.co/chernobyl\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"adsii1970","CreatedById":89014,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-14T20:54:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m on the fence about it. I was living in Hanau, West Germany when it blew. There was considerable panic when it happened. I\u0027ve held off watching the series...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tater","CreatedById":119411,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-14T20:57:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223598937\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184477\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557867240\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002289014\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022adsii1970\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, adsii1970 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m on the fence about it. I was living in Hanau, West Germany when it blew. There was considerable panic when it happened. I\u0027ve held off watching the series...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s pretty good. It\u0027s really about the response (bad, as well as good). The idiots who didn\u0027t listen from the start, the well-meaning temporizing that made it worse, and the willing sacrifice of people willing to literally do suicide missions to prevent it from being worse. Acting is great.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sh1pman","CreatedById":147869,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-14T21:09:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFun fact. Chemist Valery\u00A0Legasov\u00A0was a professor and chair of the Division\u00A0of Radiochemistry and Chemical Technology at the Chemistry Department of Moscow State University. I graduated at the same department of the same university\u00A0and now work in the building next door to the division he was administrating. He is legendary here.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"StrandedonEarth","CreatedById":89439,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-14T21:51:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n*sigh* of course I don\u0027t get that\u00A0channel. I may have to sign up to CraveTV, or use more nefarious methods\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Shpaget","CreatedById":45577,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-14T21:58:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223598935\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184477\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557867172\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022119411\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022tater\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, tater said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2 of the divers were in fact in the military, but still cool. It\u0027s just so very well done.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t really mind artistic liberties. The overall story seems to check out.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheSaint","CreatedById":70033,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-14T22:35:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223598977\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184477\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557870683\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002289439\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022StrandedonEarth\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n42 minutes ago, StrandedonEarth said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n*sigh* of course I don\u0027t get that\u00A0channel. I may have to sign up to CraveTV, or use more nefarious methods\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDitto. There\u0027s so much on streaming these days, and we watch so little TV anyway, we just don\u0027t see the point in paying a ton of money for premium stuff. Maybe it will wind up on Netflix some day.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tater","CreatedById":119411,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-14T23:24:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nit\u0027s HBO, so it won\u0027t end up on Netflix. You might be able to rent or buy it on Amazon Prime at some point, I suppose.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nuke","CreatedById":10883,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-15T00:50:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwith the way game of thrones is ending im not sure i would trust another hbo series.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nof course i was wrong about the expanse. which i avoided because of how repetitious that space opera had gotten, and yet it has turned out to be one of my favorite space shows.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-05-15T00:51:48Z\u0022 title=\u002205/15/2019 12:51  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EMay 15, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by Nuke\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-15T11:41:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, long ago, in the USSR, the light was green all day long, like in Fallout 3.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAuntie Ulya is probably a time traveller. No such character in the past found.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUpd.\u003Cbr\u003E\n2..4 Mt explosion due to a steam pressure? (s01e02, 00:50).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-05-15T12:48:44Z\u0022 title=\u002205/15/2019 12:48  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EMay 15, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by kerbiloid\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tater","CreatedById":119411,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-15T12:51:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223599053\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184477\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557881441\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002210883\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Nuke\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 hours ago, Nuke said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwith the way game of thrones is ending im not sure i would trust another hbo series.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe know how this turns out.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223599230\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184477\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557920491\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2..4 Mt explosion due to a steam pressure? (s01e02, 00:50).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI assumed they were talking about radioisotope dispersion not blast (but yeah, they could have been more clear). As it was the accident released a couple hundred times the fallout of Hiroshima, right?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-15T14:05:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223599266\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184477\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557924686\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022119411\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022tater\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, tater said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs it was the accident released a couple hundred times the fallout of Hiroshima, right?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nProbably, especially when\u00A0Hiroshima is a mid-\u00A0air blast.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Shpaget","CreatedById":45577,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-15T14:36:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#222222;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\u0022Compared with other nuclear events: The Chernobyl explosion put 400 times more radioactive material into the Earth\u0027s atmosphere than the atomic bomb dropped on Hiroshima; atomic weapons tests conducted in the 1950s and 1960s all together are estimated to have put some 100 to 1,000 times more radioactive material into the atmosphere than the Chernobyl accident.\u0022\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nfrom:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Comparison_of_Chernobyl_and_other_radioactivity_releases#Chernobyl_compared_with_an_atomic_bomb\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Comparison_of_Chernobyl_and_other_radioactivity_releases#Chernobyl_compared_with_an_atomic_bomb\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"YNM","CreatedById":98447,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-15T14:39:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHiroshima was a single instance of explosion, with all the radioactive material consumed near-instantly, while Chernobyl slowly emanated their radioactive material over the course of days by convection. The latter is larger when summed up as a whole, but not by the rate at which it was dispersing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"LordFerret","CreatedById":111598,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-15T14:42:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThings Chernobyl;\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis was on the news recently, a new \u0027video game\u0027 if you want to call it that.\u00A0 You remotely drive real RC cars through a Chernobyl city creation, post catastrophe.\u00A0 Of what I saw on the news, you pay for an hour\u0027s worth of real-time drive time.\u00A0 Pretty interesting.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/remotegames/game-with-remote-controlled-robots-over-internet\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.kickstarter.com/projects/remotegames/game-with-remote-controlled-robots-over-internet\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003EEdit:\u003C/em\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nThe site also mentions their next goal, which is a Mars environment of the same idea... driving rovers real-time in a simulated Mars environment. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-05-15T14:55:45Z\u0022 title=\u002205/15/2019 02:55  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EMay 15, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by LordFerret\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nuke","CreatedById":10883,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-15T15:48:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223599266\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184477\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557924686\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022119411\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022tater\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, tater said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe know how this turns out.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni warn you there will be zombies!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tater","CreatedById":119411,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-15T16:07:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223599371\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184477\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557935308\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002210883\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Nuke\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n18 minutes ago, Nuke said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni warn you there will be zombies!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhich will be built up as an existential threat to all life, then defeated by a young girl.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DDE","CreatedById":146349,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-15T16:12:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223598937\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184477\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557867240\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002289014\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022adsii1970\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n19 hours ago, adsii1970 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m on the fence about it. I was living in Hanau, West Germany when it blew. There was considerable panic when it happened. I\u0027ve held off watching the series...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, let me calm you down.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn May\u00A01986, the level of radionuclide exposure for children was raised about by 33 times.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022?uri=CELEX:31986R1707\u0026amp;from=DE\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022768\u0022 src=\u0022https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/PDF/?uri=CELEX:31986R1707\u0026amp;from=DE\u0022 width=\u0022541\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-16T11:44:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022344\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/1siPgAVOAtU?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022459\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EGet out of here, STALKER\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-16T19:17:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot a spoiler, as just a crowd.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022comment_K5RbNlovWZT7nWf7XqQKtZcNa6FIQZRP\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022561\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.wykop.pl/cdn/c3201142/comment_K5RbNlovWZT7nWf7XqQKtZcNa6FIQZRP,w400.jpg\u0022 width=\u0022400\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA Game of Thrones\u00A0\u00A0spoiler, caution.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022comment_htBzgt7La26fV9Ss9YyAZfPFJFwddjmd\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022362\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.wykop.pl/cdn/c3201142/comment_htBzgt7La26fV9Ss9YyAZfPFJFwddjmd,w500.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-05-16T19:27:31Z\u0022 title=\u002205/16/2019 07:27  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EMay 16, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by kerbiloid\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Cydonian Monk","CreatedById":69224,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-16T19:41:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223599230\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184477\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557920491\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 5/15/2019 at 6:41 AM, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUpd.\u003Cbr\u003E\n2..4\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E Mt e\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003Explosion due to a steam pressure? (s01e02, 00:50).\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAbout that.\u00A0While the number itself was slightly exaggerated for dramatic effect it wasn\u0027t necessarily\u00A0wrong. The short-term\u00A0release of energy would be in that ballpark, but also not instantaneous such as a single detonation event. It also wasn\u0027t just the number for a steam explosion - it was for a somewhat smaller\u00A0steam explosion resulting in a cascade event ending with loss of control and potential explosion\u00A0of the other three functioning cores; the combined effect of which would be in the several megaton range.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThink about how many windows broke due to the relatively tiny Chelyabinsk meteor, that was in the 500 kiloton range. The initial damage probably would not have\u00A0been\u00A0much more severe than that in Minsk and/or\u00A0Kiev\u00A0even up to ~4 megaton, if you ignore\u00A0all the radioactive fallout.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere was some discussion over on reddit with the show runner about this point (I don\u0027t recall the specific\u00A0discussion or I\u0027d link to it). From a technical point of view it\u0027s a good catch; general audience would just gloss their eyes over it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-05-16T20:51:13Z\u0022 title=\u002205/16/2019 08:51  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EMay 16, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by Cydonian Monk\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EEdit: Changed two reactors to three.\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}